						<summary>

						<p>On the north wall of the Veṅkaṭēśa-perumāḷ temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vīrarājēndradēva: Year 10 = 1216-17 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription records a grant of land in Kaṇṇāḍipputtūr to a <hi rend="italic">maṭha</hi> (name not clear) in the Adirājēndran-tirumaḍai-viḷāgam in Koḻumam by Gaṅgan-śōḻan Aṇukkappallavaraiyan <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Aṇukkanambi of Eḻśilūr in Karaivaḻi-nāḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
